<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #179299; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to PodRead!</h1>

    <p>Someone thinks you'd enjoy this — you've been given a complimentary PodRead account.</p>

    <p>PodRead turns articles, blog posts, and notes into audio — and creates a personal podcast feed you can listen to in your favorite podcast app. Here's what's included with your account:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Unlimited episodes</strong> each month</li>
      <li><strong>Up to 50,000 characters</strong> per episode</li>
      <li><strong>12 voices</strong> to choose from, including our highest quality voices</li>
      <li><strong>Share and download</strong> your episodes</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @magic_link_url %>" class="button">Log in and get started</a>
    </p>

    <p>To create a new episode, just paste a URL, paste text, or upload a file at <a href="https://podread.app">podread.app</a>.</p>

    <p>This link expires in 30 minutes. Once you're in, you can request a new login link anytime from the home page.</p>

    <p>We hope you love it. And if you do, tell your friends!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
